<div class="title">I Love My Father Again</div>
<div class="substance">Ayahuasca (B. caapi & P. viridis) & Ritual</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Osta&Exact=1">Osta</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Osta. "I Love My Father Again: An Experience with Ayahuasca (B. caapi & P. viridis) & Ritual (exp80647)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 31, 2009. erowid.org/exp/80647</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

